args: YEAAAH! Let's pluck this turkey, chariot!
Hah! Didja see that, Slick? I sent that\nwimp flyin'!
So you did. Keep it up, Yuya.
Heh. Me and my chariot have GOT\nthi—wha?!
Holy mackerel... That's one big turkey!
Urgh! He knocked me off my chariot!\nGotta get back on...
Sorry, Slick. Without my chariot, I can't...
Looks like it's just you and me,\n{player_name}! Haaaah!
Jeez... You guys finished him in one hit?
It's not as impressive as it looked.
Yeah. That fiend was all bark.
No foolin'? Then I let a wimpy fiend\nscare me...?
I haven't grown a lick since the time\nRed Champ saved my tail!
What, you've never heard of him?\nHe's ginormous, and the strongest\ncat around!
Just lookin' in his eyes had me AND the\nfiends shakin' in our boots.
I have the same effect on buffets. Ha ha!
Well, whoever he is, he saved you from\nfiends. Is that right?
Yup. That's when I decided I wanted to\nbecome big and strong, just like him.
I even changed up my duds and combed\nmy hair to match his!
Yer tellin' me other people dress like\nthat too?
Oh, he looks aces. Big and red\nand FLASHY!
And man, that voice.\nFull'a fire, I'm tellin' ya!
All'a that in such a tiny body.\nI dunno how he does it!
Er, didn't you just say he was big?
He is! He's small, yet so big!
Not quite, but I can at least understand\nwanting to be like the person you admire.
I'm sure you'll be more like Red Champ\none day, Yuya. Don't worry.
Heh! Thanks, Slick. Glad to know you've\ngot my back.
And hey, maybe you can learn to be\nlike him too!
I-I'm fine as I am, I think.
They won't scare me this time.\nI'm gonna knock 'em flat!
Fiends I can understand, but are ya tellin'\nme yer afraid'a chickens, too?
I can't believe it... What're you DOIN' here,\nRed Champ?!
No way. There's no way Red Champ is\na damn chicken.
But Ranzal, look at his comb...
It DOES look a lot like Yuya.
Jeez, ya actually have a point. But hang\non... If that's Red Champ, and Red Champ\nis his idol, then...his idol's a chicken?
If he saved Yuya from fiends, he must be\nquite strong.
Oh man, peep those peepers...\nHe is fired UP!
You're the coolest, Red Champ.\nWho'd ya beat up on the way here?
Ha ha, you're the best, Red Champ!
And yet you keep up the conversation...
Er, Ranzal? What are you doing?
Shhh, lemme see what he says.
Seriously? Damn, that's the bee's knees!
Hah, he got it! Kid's full'a hidden talents.\nCluckity cluck cluck!
Ha ha, I KNEW you guys'd get along!
